{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a5976ebc7","title":"周恩来接见外交部各组织代表的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9e452894b4","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"8a5976ebc7"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c3cc0323df","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见外交部各组织代表的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"fdc68c1c84","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"e1f166b741","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月一日，总理接见了外交部各组织的代表。参加接见的有陈毅及其他部党委成员，刘晓未参加。接见情况如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"56ed0e6ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"1、使馆在十二月份要立即办毛泽东思想学习班；","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"4f7ca92689","type":"paragraph","text":"2、对外交部东方红兵团（67.11.30成立的，属“外联”34战斗队一派）没表态，总理说：“东方红兵团声明很弱，政治主张不明确。”","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"2f5d7cd963","type":"paragraph","text":"3、对“外联”34战斗队没表态。34战斗队代表曾发表意见，但被到会代表压了下去。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"fd8c5d9ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"4、总理说：“业务监督小组暂时不要动，同志们要负起责任来，加强自信，把工作搞好。大联筹对他们的态度是正确的（指没有撤换监督人员）要斗私批修，学毛选。正确对待34个战斗队的群众。”","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"361650ba0a","type":"paragraph","text":"5、总理说：“对516不要认为中共中央非常委员会有线索就认为没事了，还是有坏人的，要注意阶级斗争。”外交部自王焕德揪出后，又搞出了个泄密小集团。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"96b2665e02","type":"paragraph","text":"6、总理还批评陈毅说：“你在北戴河会议上反王稼祥的“三和一少”是好的，但到广州会议就变了。”","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"20a46bdeb8","type":"paragraph","text":"参加接见的还有王海蓉、唐闻生（唐明照的女儿）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"},{"id":"ca8f17154e","type":"paragraph","text":"（据外交口同志传达，非记录，供参考）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7"}],"page":{"id":"2a6ffaae5f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a5976ebc7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}